I pass through the entrance to the elementary school grounds. [p]
When I open the door that leads into the school building, I see that even more darkness is waiting for me inside.[p]
It is possible that Cheryl scribbled those letters "to School."[p]
I can't be sure whether Cheryl is here or not.[p]
It's just that I haven't a clue other than that sketchbook.[p]
A guide map of the school has been tacked to the sidewall of the entrance with a rusted thumbtack.[p]
After removing the map from the wall, I place it in my pocket and push open the heavy door that leads [p]
into the interior of the school building.[p]


