When I open the door, I see that the inside of the room is large and there is a grand piano placed in its center.[p]
As I sit on the chair of the piano I am shocked.[p]
The seat is still warm, as if someone had been sitting here just a few minutes before.[p]
Cheryl's smile runs through the back of my mind.[p]
Cheryl often played the cheap upright piano in our home.[p]
It had become nice background music when I was working.[p]
Perhaps Cheryl had come to the music room?[p]


[bg  time="200"  method="crossfade"  storage="BLACK.gif"  ]
