The sleety mixture of snow pounds hard against the windows facing the courtyard.[p]
I take a look through a window down at the dark courtyard.[p]
The not so large courtyard is dotted with areas in which withered plants are growing. [p]
In addition to that, an old clock tower is faintly visible.[p]
From here, I cannot determine what time the clock is pointing to.[p]


